## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **voxelotor Oxbryta 2019** = first HbS polymerization inhibitor — α-chain N-terminal allosteric covalent. HbS T-state stabilization. quantum-VQE 의 hemoglobin allosteric pocket 직접 fit. 2024 postmarketing safety signal (EMA 우려) — context 변동.
2. **Casgevy + Lyfgenia 2023 동반 승인** = first ex-vivo CRISPR (BCL11A erythroid enhancer guide) + second lentivirus (β-globin transgene) — sickle cell + β-thal 적응증 공유. 2-3M USD per patient, ex-vivo HSC editing 인프라 hospital constraint.
3. **mitapivat Pyrukynd 2022 + 2024 thal expansion** = first FDA pyruvate kinase deficiency + α/β-thalassemia expansion. PK-R allosteric activator → 2,3-BPG 감소 + ATP 증가 → RBC membrane integrity. quantum-VQE allosteric pocket leverage. SCD phase 3 ongoing.
4. **emicizumab Hemlibra 2017** = first FVIII-mimetic bispecific antibody (FIXa + FX bridging). hemophilia A inhibitor + non-inhibitor 적응증 확장. subQ administration paradigm shift.
5. **Roctavian 2023 + Hemgenix 2022** = AAV5-based hemophilia A + B in-vivo gene therapy. 단회 infusion → multi-year FVIII/IX expression. liver tropism + neutralizing AAV antibody screening 필요. 3.5M USD (Hemgenix world-most-expensive).
6. **fitusiran (AT siRNA, Sanofi 2024 BLA) + concizumab (TFPI mAb 2024 pending)** = "rebalancing" 패러다임 — factor replacement 대신 inhibitor pathway 억제로 hemostasis 균형. inhibitor-positive hem A+B 모두 fit. clot risk 균형 가는 임상 challenge.
7. **caplacizumab Cablivi 2019** = first nanobody FDA — vWF A1 도메인 + plasma exchange 보조 aTTP. ADAMTS13 활성 회복 동안 microthrombus 차단. nanobody platform leverage.
8. **crizanlizumab Adakveo 2019** = first P-selectin mAb VOC reduction SCD. 2023 postmarketing STAND trial primary endpoint miss → EMA 승인 철회 + FDA 재검토 진행. quantum-VQE 의 falsifier candidate 로 적합 — postmarketing 의문 검증.
9. **fostamatinib Tavalisse 2018 + avatrombopag 2018 + lusutrombopag 2018 + rilzabrutinib research** = ITP 2017-2024 폭발기. Syk + TPO-RA + BTK 다축 — 기존 corticosteroid + IVIG + splenectomy + rituximab paradigm 의 보조/대체.
10. **asundexian + abelacimab + milvexian factor XIa class (research-stage)** = anticoagulation safer-target paradigm — XIa 억제 시 thrombosis 차단 but hemostasis 비교적 보존. AF + VTE phase 3 ongoing 2024-2026, 차세대 anticoagulant 후보.

